<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   1.)  The chance for crit has been removed from the skill.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  it will never crit again.  ok, that's not much of a nerf I guess.  I mean hell... I didn't crit it much anyway.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   2.) Mobs under 33k hp have been flagged &quot;Unburnable&quot;.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Yeah, that's the bad one.  I rather liked using MB all the time, like hell when I'm XPing and bored.  but no more...  How lame.<br>
<br>
<br>
Anyone else know what VI was thinking when they decided to do this?  I for one would really like to know.<br>
<br>
